    "Details": "Created by The Republic of the Sphere this variant of the MHI Amphibious APC sacrifices the infantry bay for a larger Light Fusion engine, allowing it to reach a top speed of 96 km/h. It retains the ER Medium Laser and actually increases armament by adding a pair of Light Machine Guns to the turret. The tank is protected by seven and a half tons of Heavy Ferro-Fibrous armor and an Angel ECM Suite. The Full Amphibious Equipment is also present. The most deadly feature is the Drone Carrier Control System.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Fusion: Expensive engine that works in a Vacuum.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 6/9 Hex: 180/270 Meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Heavy Ferro-Fibrous\n<b>Structure:</b> Environmental Sealing\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       225     20\n<b>Left</b>         155     20\n<b>Right</b>       155     20\n<b>Rear</b>        115     20\n<b>Turret</b>      155     20\n\n<b>Total</b>      805    100</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Narrow/Low Profile</color>",
